unittitle_ssm: Records of the John Frost Library Collection
abstract_ssm: The John Frost Library collection contains the administrative files of John Frost, who served as head librarian of the Gould Memorial Library at the University Heights campus between 1955-1972 and as a member of the library faculty from 1972-1982. The collection contains administrative files, including correspondence, committee meeting minutes, reports, publications and library floor plans.
